      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The private residence of Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe in Cinnamon Gardens has been set on fire.",
        "Meanwhile, several media persons were attacked by the Special Task Force officers, while reporting the demonstration staged outside the PM\u2019s residence."
